description: Adds or overwrites one or more tags for the specified CloudHSM cluster. Cross-account use: No. You cannot perform this operation on an CloudHSM resource in a different Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: ResourceId
parameters.description: The cluster identifier (ID) for the cluster that you are tagging. To find the cluster ID, use  DescribeClusters.

parameters.name: TagList
parameters.description: A list of one or more tags. (dict) --- Contains a tag. A tag is a key-value pair. The key of the tag. The value of the tag.
